name: Get Rich or Die Trying
description: $GRODT is more than just a meme token, it’s a movement born from the trenches of crypto where risk, humor, and ambition collide. Every wallet in the grind knows the truth: this space is not for the faint of heart, it’s for those bold enough to chase generational wealth with full conviction. We are here to embrace the highs, endure the lows, and live by the mantra that defines every true degen: get rich or die trying. With $GRODT, the culture becomes the currency.
